        "title": "Petroleum and Natural Gas Ministry refutes claims that Bhutan declined offer to import E20 petrol from India are incorrect",
        "summary": "Ministry of Petroleum and Natural Gas has refuted claims circulating on social media that Bhutan declined an offer to import E20 petrol from India are incorrect. The Ministry said that the reports are incorrect and no such offer has been made by the Oil Marketing Companies. It said there is no proposal for the export […]",
        "article": "Ministry of Petroleum and Natural Gas has refuted claims circulating on social media that Bhutan declined an offer to import E20 petrol from India are incorrect. The Ministry said that the reports are incorrect and no such offer has been made by the Oil Marketing Companies. It said there is no proposal for the export of E20 petrol to Bhutan. It has asked citizens to rely only on official information from the Ministry and the Oil Marketing Companies.",
